event.title: Free Software and GNU/Linux enthusiasts meeting in Minsk, Belarus

body.p: Minsk GNU/Linux and Free Software enthusiasts have not been enjoyed meetings in person for a long time. This is an attempt to revive the tradition to meet in person. The FSFE local group Minsk will be there! The event takes place in Russian, at 11:00. The address is Pijanierskaja str. 5a, Haradzišča, Minsk district, Belarus.
